main event: A civilian reported a UFO sighting of an unidentified square object larger than a football field in Bedford, Virginia on January 25, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as being aluminum and glowing in the middle., The observer saw the object at a 30-degree elevation, and it appeared to be hovering., The sighting lasted for 3-5 minutes before the object disappeared., The weather conditions were clear, with no clouds present at the time of the sighting., There were two separate UFO sightings reported in the same timeframe in the nearby area.
sighted object: one square object larger than a football field
